<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='768000' id='t-768000'>That's the main use of that filter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770000' id='t-770000'>Venus, of course, is the god of love and fertility,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='773000' id='t-773000'>which is the flower story.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='775000' id='t-775000'>And just as flowers spend a lot of effort</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='777000' id='t-777000'>trying to get pollinators to do their bidding,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='780000' id='t-780000'>they've also somehow managed to persuade us to plant great fields full of them</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='783000' id='t-783000'>and give them to each other</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='785000' id='t-785000'>at times of birth and death,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789000' id='t-789000'>and particularly at marriage,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='791000' id='t-791000'>which, when you think of it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='793000' id='t-793000'>is the moment that encapsulates</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='795000' id='t-795000'>the transfer of genetic material</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='798000' id='t-798000'>from one organism to another.</span>
</span>
</p>
